text: Mikhaylovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Denisovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 140 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Meleuz, 6 km from Bogorodskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Mikhaylovka, Meleuzovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
